summary.raw: remove ogre gl texture header, add opengl checks, merge custom pssm files, fix code check errors

values.message: remove ogre gl texture header, add opengl checks, merge custom pssm files, fix code check errors

summary.raw: Renamed shadow function in shader. Use Poisson filter that has one sample in center.
summary.html: Renamed shadow function in shader. Use Poisson filter that has one sample in center.

values.message: Renamed shadow function in shader. Use Poisson filter that has one sample in center.

summary.raw: Added some API so that shadows can be tuned through plugins.
summary.html: Added some API so that shadows can be tuned through plugins.

values.message: Added some API so that shadows can be tuned through plugins.

summary.raw: Comment out some more unused shadow code.
summary.html: Comment out some more unused shadow code.

values.message: Comment out some more unused shadow code.

summary.raw: Light everything outside shadowmaps' depth range, so we no longer need to cut off shadow at shadowFarDistance. This lets more of the farthest shadow map be used.
summary.html: Light everything outside shadowmaps' depth range, so we no longer need to cut off shadow at shadowFarDistance. This lets more of the farthest shadow map be used.

values.message: Light everything outside shadowmaps' depth range, so we no longer need to cut off shadow at shadowFarDistance. This lets more of the farthest shadow map be used.

summary.raw: Cut off shadows at shadowFarDistance so that everything beyond that point is lit.
summary.html: Cut off shadows at shadowFarDistance so that everything beyond that point is lit.

values.message: Cut off shadows at shadowFarDistance so that everything beyond that point is lit.

summary.raw: Tuned shadowFarDistance and PSSM split point lambda.
summary.html: Tuned shadowFarDistance and PSSM split point lambda.

values.message: Tuned shadowFarDistance and PSSM split point lambda.

summary.raw: Changed PSSM shadows to take advantage of hardare PCF, a driver hack that provides 4-sample interpolated shadow edges. Changed shader to use hardware PCF and a 9-sample Poisson disk filter for shadow smoothing.
summary.html: Changed PSSM shadows to take advantage of hardare PCF, a driver hack that provides 4-sample interpolated shadow edges. Changed shader to use hardware PCF and a 9-sample Poisson disk filter for shadow smoothing.

values.message: Changed PSSM shadows to take advantage of hardare PCF, a driver hack that provides 4-sample interpolated shadow edges. Changed shader to use hardware PCF and a 9-sample Poisson disk filter for shadow smoothing.

summary.raw: PSSM shadows use modified Focused shadows that align shadow frusta with z-up instead of using LiSPSM shadows.
summary.html: PSSM shadows use modified Focused shadows that align shadow frusta with z-up instead of using LiSPSM shadows.

values.message: PSSM shadows use modified Focused shadows that align shadow frusta with z-up instead of using LiSPSM shadows.
